BasicDetails.Description:

Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath in Tucson's Civano Community! Enjoy a perfect entertaining kitchen with eat in breakfast bar, large center island, TONS of cabinet/counter space, and beautiful wood-like cabinetry! Spacious living room area with cozy fireplace and tile flooring throughout. Great size bedrooms. Gorgeous backyard features turf mini golf, covered patio, and easy to maintain desert landscaping! Civano is a sought out Tucson community with resident access to community pools, tennis courts, playgrounds, nursery, and beautiful surrounding mountain views. Close proximity to great Vail school district, variety of east-side restaurants, stores, and retailers!

Pets are allowed, and this is a perfect home for those who love spending time with their furry friends! In addition to the adorable condo unit, the house also includes a washer and dryer, parking, and a deck. The high ceilings and large closets will make you feel like you're living in your own private space. The wood burning fireplace is perfect for taking the chill out on cold winter evenings. BasicDetails.Description: Come check out his spacious three-bedroom, three-bath duplex condo for rent in Uptown! Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops with wood cabinets, and an island. The primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom w/ jacuzzi, shower and a sun-drenched porch. The bottom floor has a large rec. room perfect for a peloton/exercise equipment or just relaxing! The second bedroom features Jack and Jill bathroom with his & hers sinks with gorgeous countertops. This location boasts a 90 walk score and is accessible to the 81, 136, 146, and 148 bus routes, as well as the Wilson & Argyle Red line stops, will make commuting a breeze! Enjoy some of the best music venues in the city, such as the Byline Bank Aragon Ballroom and Riviera Theater are just blocks away. Puptown Dog park, soccer & baseball fields, and Montrose Beach are just across Lake Shore Drive. This unit comes with an exterior tandem parking space for two cars! Pets welcome w/ weight restrictions! Contact us to schedule a showing.

BasicDetails.Title: Beautiful 3/2 Spacious Home with a Large Florida Room in Villas of Casselberry - Winter Park!
BasicDetails.Description: Beautiful 3/2 Spacious Home with a Large Florida Room in Villas of Casselberry - Winter Park! Available Now! The vibrant community Villas of Casselberry offers a range of recreational activities and cultural events to keep you engaged. Welcome to this beautiful home located in the heart of Casselberry and Winter Park! This recently remodeled home offers a spacious floor plan with a bright and airy living space. Adding to the comfort and style, tile flooring flows throughout the home. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a welcoming atmosphere for both relaxation and entertaining. The modern kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and beautiful dark wood cabinets with plenty of storage space, making it a chef's delight. The sliding doors lead you off to a common area that is a large enclosed Florida Room with air conditioning! Perfect for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply unwinding after a long day. The bedroom layout provides space and comfort for everybody. The master suite is a private retreat, featuring a spacious bedroom with a large closet and an ensuite bathroom. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms with ample closet space and a shared bathroom, offer versatility for guests or a growing family. You can use one of the bedrooms as a home office, studio or playroom. The stylish second bathroom is designed with both functionality and aesthetics in mind. For added convenience this home offers an inside utility closet (Washer and Dryer Hook-ups only) and a spacious driveway for parking. Great location, only 10 minutes to Rollins College, and 7 minutes to Full Sail University, close to all major roads and highways, which offer a range of shopping, restaurants and entertainment options. Pets will be considered. NO SIGHT UNSEEN APPLICATIONS. Contact us to schedule a showing.

BasicDetails.Title: Well Known two bedroom with ample space - available now
BasicDetails.Description: Welcome to your new home at 3516 North Hamlin Avenue! This charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo is now available for rent. With its convenient location and desirable features, this property offers a comfortable and modern living experience. Step inside and be greeted by the beautiful hardwood floors that flow throughout the unit. The open layout creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing after a long day. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, providing ample space for meal preparation, and a dishwasher for easy clean-up. One of the standout features of this condo is the in-unit washer and dryer, ensuring that laundry day is a breeze. Additionally, residents can enjoy the fresh air and city views from their own private balcony. Parking is made easy with permit street parking available in the area. Whether you prefer to commute by car or public transportation, this location has you covered. Nearby bus stops and train stations provide convenient access to all that Chicago has to offer. Pets are welcome. Contact us to schedule a showing.

Available January 1st!!! Contact us to schedule a showing.

With its beautiful flooring and ample natural light, this home offers a warm and inviting atmosphere, accentuated by a cozy fireplace in the spacious living room.
